{"type": "article", "id": 9776, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-05-20T08:05:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7612, "name": "Disney"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 1270, "name": "Airbnb"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 76, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155852ye10g6XJKRT542Pq.png", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">Airbnb On River Thames by Airbnb </span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">Airbnb 近日推出了一个“水上漂浮屋”，位置是英国的泰晤士河上，屋子里设有一间客厅，两间卧室以及洗手间。而室外则有一座小花园，一个狗屋和一棵苹果树。这意味着，你甚至可以带上你的小狗去泰晤士河上发呆了。小屋将会从 5 月 22 日开始沿着泰晤士河一路漂流。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144717Sh9n76waubjs1B2T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061447188KErLk6tnHIMu1Ol.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144718TIjaVEOMw9fKyWkr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060614471959baijEYyDVNpmn0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061447194hBqbXEykHA7Tzpx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144720su3wE7dSmFtqPVDk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144720IJxfYq25ZVglk0hO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144721GBIsnj0HTzKoEOqY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tLight Phone by Joe Holler &amp; Kaiwei Tang\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">Light Phone 是一款“反智能”的手机，它诞生于谷歌 30 Weeks 发起的设计师孵化器，来自艺术家 Joe Holler 和产品设计师 Kaiwei Tang。这款手机能做什么？答案是除了接打电话什么都不能。一次充电后可以满足 20 天左右的续航。“返璞归真”的手机不管从概念还是产品来讲都不少见，但能做的这么好看的还真不多。目前产品售价 100 美元，正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，感兴趣的话可以<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/thelightphone/the-light-phone\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里支持</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060614472134KFMYxDdwjZy5of.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74572127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061447227HAGRSBNkvzPfcZJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061447229E8qskW3JR4PiMzT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64792176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144723rgZ8np5DosPLOl1v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63325183\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144723yo8J3lzKWUcnZQRr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56356968\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144724HLMWZsraAQqV780c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63447433\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144724KOuowzWU93NHL2V6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">hsbLABS by hsbCAD</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">hsbCAD 工作室最近推出了一个可以帮助建筑设计师把平面设计方案变为 3D 立体模型的应用程序，名字叫做 “hsbLABS”。他们使用应用程序，将建筑草图分解成不同的部分，再通过 3D 打印机打印出来之后进行拼接。这款程序不需要其他的用具辅助，只需打印材料和颜料，便可以打印出立体的 3D 建筑模板。<a href=\"http://www.hsblabs.com/#target\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061447242QbjDmeM5Nq3cYt0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52689487\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144725rgMziqtBcxdvspfG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5391198\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144725eyuAJmIq8VRX7wKC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53789731\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144726f1CrX5wZml96sGLv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061447264NQuSlRsh6U5Ji2d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54278729\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144727YqObVaJsLpRgXUSc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48899756\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">Italic Light by COORDINATION-berlin</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">这款意大利灯由 COORDINATION-berlin 在 2015 年米兰设计周期间展出，灯的外部是一个大理石外壳，光束透过大理石内部放射出来，内置的是一个 LED 循环灯环，一个内置转换器和一个纺织电缆。灯具遵循极简主义设计风格，大理石的白和蓝色的配色看上去简单优雅。这是 <a href=\"http://www.coordination-berlin.com/?lang=en\" target=\"_blank\">COORDINATION-berlin 的官方主页</a>，感兴趣的话可以查看他们更多信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144727qGtLw8siPHOpdvYF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9193154\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061447286eBnKpLI1F23MrV9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88997555\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144728hqbg4tomvE3LUfKZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144729Y3spDxlvtybHnAfQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3997555\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144729NkvCsu2eMa5qOcKj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.12224939\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144729kFRhjAZgUdumapQT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09046455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tYoung at Heart by Disney &amp; Vans \r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">Disney 最近与 Vans 推出了一个新的联名系列，这个名为 “Young at Heart” 的系列在风格上和其名字一样动感十足，他们把 Disney 经典的卡通形象，如米老鼠，唐老鸭，维尼小熊等印制在了 Vans 经典的“一脚蹬”以及书包，帆布鞋，袜子等产品上面，营造出浓浓的夏日可爱风。这个联名系列将在 6 月正式登陆 Vans 全球指定店铺。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144730N06BQY9Afokg8J7i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144730USNPGu6ZWYmRhErA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144731fJGVd6Zl9chHPDtM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144731LWwBrTlV0goEeXfN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144732uoDk8j5MCWPLegb2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">Hot Milk Lab by Sebastian Bergne </span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">设计师 Sebastian Bergne 最近推出了一个“迷你实验室”，方便人们制作各种饮料。其中 Hot Milk Lab 专门方便人们在热牛奶里面加入各种配料，制作出不同风味的饮料。Sebastian Bergne 的这一套实验室由木制的托盘和不同型号的玻璃瓶，酒精灯以及托盘组成，烧牛奶的玻璃瓶中放置了一个温度计，可以方便使用者调节温度。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144732bWRzP3cUi7OyQmGx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144733QS09lxIPBgF3utki.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144733wqnul1kSpRLa3G7r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144734UE95cerbYu8h4ZQB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061447340dUYFlznv8cirONs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144735y1BJACl2xMdSFc57.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144735DL8U6qh5fyC7YTQR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144736FpRtluPnUyq6s3jm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}